data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Minutes from Fort Cavazos, restaurants and shopping; nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers the perfect balance of comfort and sophistication. As you approach, you'll be captivated by the charming curb appeal and manicured landscaping. Step inside, and you'll discover a spacious and well-designed floor plan. The main floor boasts 2 living spaces and 2 dining areas perfect for entertaining guests formally and casually. The kitchen is equipped with ample counter space, double ovens, flat cook top and refrigerator. A open and convenient breakfast area for casual dining that is open to the living space. The walk-in pantry/ laundry space possess ample shelving, utility sink, and still gives additional space for washer/dryer. The second floor hosts four generously sized bedrooms, each offering a retreat-like atmosphere. The primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a luxurious ensuite bathroom with separate shower, jacuzzi tub and walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms provide versatility, whether you need a home office, guest room, or space for a growing family.
Throughout the home, large windows flood each room with natural light, creating an airy and uplifting ambiance.
Step outside into the private backyard oasis with a covered patio perfect for entertaining, or simply unwinding after a long day. The outdoor space is complemented by lush landscaping and a shed. This home is equipped with modern amenities, a new roof (Jan 2023) with life time warranty, and energy-efficient features, ensuring both comfort and sustainability with a two-car garage and ample storage space, practicality meets style in every aspect of this residence.
 
Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite house your new home sweet home for the holidays! Schedule your showing today and experience the beauty and comfort that awaits you.
